 a_{1},a_{2},....,a_{n}(n\geq 3) 
(a_{1}+a_{2}+....+a_{n})^2 >\frac{3n-1}{3}(a_{1}^2+a_{2}^2+....+a_{n}^2)
a_{i},a_{j},a_{k} 
 i,j,k 
 0< i< j< k\leq n 
n=3
a_1,\dots,a_n
a_1+a_2>a_3
n=3
n=3
(a_1+a_2)^2>a_3^2
2\left((a_1+a_2)^2+a_3^2\right)\ge \left((a_1+a_2)+a_3\right)^2 \quad{and}\quad a_1^2+a_2^2\ge \frac{1}{2}(a_1+a_2)^2.
n>3
\frac{3n-1}{3}=\frac{8}{3}+n-3
n=3
a_1+\dots+a_n=\sqrt{\frac{8}{3}}\times\sqrt{\frac{3}{8}}(a_1+a_2+a_3)+1\times a_4+\dots+1\times a_n.
\frac{3n-1}{3}\left(\frac{3}{8}(a_1+a_2+a_3)^2+a_4^2+\dots+a_n^2\right)\ge(a_1+\dots+a_n)^2.
